{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bold Blue Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #00008B; /* Dark Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #ADD8E6; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n            --accent-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 139, 0.7), rgba(70, 130, 180, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/00008B/FFFFFF?text=Bold+Blue+Realty') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .features, .about, .contact {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h3, .about h3, .contact h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for Icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Bold Blue Realty</h1>\n            <p>Your Vision, Our Expertise.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Dream Home</h2>\n            <p>Unlocking Doors to Exceptional Living</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"properties\" class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Featured Properties</h3>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-home\"></i>\n                    <h4>Modern Condo</h4>\n                    <p>Sleek design, prime location. <br> Contact for details.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-house-user\"></i>\n                    <h4>Family House</h4>\n                    <p>Spacious, quiet neighborhood. <br> Perfect for growth.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-building\"></i>\n                    <h4>Commercial Space</h4>\n                    <p>High-traffic area. <br> Ideal for your business.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Bold Blue Realty</h3>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>At Bold Blue Realty, we are driven by a passion for real estate and a commitment to excellence. Our team of dedicated professionals leverages deep market knowledge and innovative strategies to help clients navigate the complexities of buying, selling, and investing in property. We believe in transparency, integrity, and building lasting relationships.</p>\n                <p>We specialize in residential and commercial properties, offering personalized service tailored to your unique needs. Let us guide you to your next significant investment or your perfect sanctuary.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Bold Blue Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! Thank you for contacting Bold Blue Realty.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}